title: 157: DJ's Mock Draft 2.0, scouting winning culture
itunes:title: 157: DJ's Mock Draft 2.0, scouting winning culture
description:
Daniel Jeremiah reveals his second mock draft of the season and breaks it down with Bucky Brooks. DJ and Bucky discuss locker room culture and how winning and new technology can impact that. The duo also makes the tough comparisons between QBs, RBs, LBs and others prospects for the 2017 NFL Draft.
